"signal_description": "Calculate the average time taken to change the status of a bug issue to 'In Progress' after it was created. The query is performed on the 'defaultview-217' table. The 'IssueType' column is used to filter only the bug issues. The calculation is done by subtracting the timestamp of the first 'Create Issue' event from the timestamp of the last 'Change Status to In Progress' event for each bug issue, and then taking the average of these differences."
